column30:
You are being asked to participate in a research study.

 

The purpose of the study is to learn about everyday experiences and individual differences between people. We are interested in your perceptions about several leisure activities. You will be asked to answer a series of questions about yourself and your everyday experiences.

 

Your participation is voluntary. You can skip any question you do not wish to answer or withdraw at any time. You must be 18 or older to participate. If you have any questions please contact Dr. Nancy Rhodes, at rhodesn3@msu.edu.
